"622","<TEXT>"
"623","SUB-ITEM 77E.  LEGAL PROCEEDINGS"
"624","Since February 2004, Federated and related"
"625","entities (collectively, Federated) have been"
"626","named as defendants in several lawsuits, that"
"627","were consolidated into a single action in the"
"628","United States District Court for the Western"
"629","District of Pennsylvania, alleging excessive advisory"
"630","fees involving one of the Federated-sponsored"
"631","mutual funds.  Without admitting the validity of"
"632","any claim, Federated reached a final settlement"
"633","with the Plaintiffs in these cases in April 2011."
"634","	- 1 -"
"635","</TEXT>"
"636","</DOCUMENT>"
"637","</SEC-DOCUMENT>"
